4Geeks Academy offers a course in Applied Artificial Intelligence. This course provides a detailed exploration of artificial intelligence and how it can be applied in different industries and roles. It is a 6-week program that requires no previous knowledge. The course covers various topics, including generative AI, context, prompts, and models. Students will learn essential tools and best practices to optimize AI integration. The class size is limited to 12 people, and there are two live, online classes per week. Upon completion, students will receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate recognized by multiple institutions. To learn more, visit their website at [https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/applied-ai-course](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/applied-ai-course). stop